    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="man_ej.00096_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <date when="1880-06-21"><hi rend="underline">6<hi rend="superscript">th</hi>
                                21<hi rend="superscript">th</hi> 1880</hi></date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>My Dear Walt:</salute></opener>

            <p>I send you my political letter from the Post<ptr target="n1049"/>&#8212;</p>

            <p>Tell me how you like it</p>
            <p><choice><orig>Johnson</orig><reg>Johnston</reg></choice><ptr target="n0335"/> called here Sunday with your letter to his Boy.<ptr target="man.00039_n1"/></p>
            <p>Now take a little
                    advice from me.
                You are <hi rend="underline">wise</hi> I know. I am <hi rend="underline"
                    >otherwise</hi>. <pb xml:id="leaf002r" facs="man_ej.00206_large.jpg"
                    type="verso"/>But it is Mrs <hi rend="underline"><choice><orig>Johnson</orig><reg>Johnston</reg></choice></hi> who seems most
                hurt&#8212;&amp; she has been very kind to you&#8212;</p>

            <p>Now if I was Walt
                Whitman I <choice>
                    <abbr>w<hi rend="superscript">d</hi></abbr>
                    <expan>would</expan>
                </choice> write to her &amp; say all the pleasant things I <choice>
                    <abbr>c<hi rend="superscript">d</hi></abbr>
                    <expan>could</expan>
                </choice> of the past&#8212;say I was sorry there was any misunderstanding&#8212;you know what to say&#8212;</p>
            <p>I think they are poor&#8212;&amp; feel very <hi rend="underline">very</hi>
                <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#nhg">badly</unclear> over it indeed&#8212;such a
                letter <choice>
                    <abbr>w<hi rend="superscript">d</hi></abbr>
                    <expan>would</expan>
                </choice>
                stop <choice><orig>Johnson</orig><reg>Johnston</reg></choice>s
                blathering&#8212;for it don't matter much what he
                says</p>

            <closer>
                <salute>As ever yours</salute>
                <signed>J M Scovel</signed>
            </closer>
            <pb xml:id="leaf002v" facs="man_ej.00097_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
            <postscript><p>PS We are all glad you are having so nice a time &amp; send <gap reason="illegible" extent="one word" unit="chars"
                    quantity="6"/> regards&#8212;</p></postscript>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="man_ej.00098_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
        </body>
